OL,3,CRacist attack victim living in fear of
OL,4,Cfamily
OL,6,FA man who had racist graffiti spray-
OL,7,Fpainted on the side of his home in
OL,8,FBallykelly, says he feels nervous and
OL,9,Fhas considered leaving his own home.
OL,11,FShinu Mathew, who lives with his wife
OL,12,Fand two young girls says he is worried
OL,13,Fabout his family's safety.
OL,15,FGraffiti was painted on a number of
OL,16,Fhomes in Fort Drive and Forest Drive
OL,17,Fin the County Londonderry village
OL,18,Faround 3am on Tuesday.
OL,20,FPolice said it was being treated as a
OL,21,Fhate crime.
