OL,6,FMr Mathew says he woke up at 8am and
OL,7,Fsaw someone had spray-painted the
OL,8,Fracist remarks.
OL,10,FHe said he did not know how serious
OL,11,Fthe writing was until his neighbours
OL,12,Ftold him that the people who did it
OL,13,Fwere trying to force them to leave.
OL,15,FMr Mathew says "That night (after the
OL,16,Fattack) I didn't sleep. I heard some
OL,17,Fnoises and kept checking the window."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
