OL,6,F"I am worried, because I am working
OL,7,Fnightshift, and two or three times I
OL,8,Fcall my wife to see if there is any
OL,9,Fproblems."
OL,11,FMr Mathew however, says his neighbours
OL,12,Fhave been very supportive and came
OL,13,Ftogether to wash away the graffiti.
OL,15,F"Not expecting this, because I like
OL,16,Fthis place it is very quiet. My
OL,17,Frelatives are living in Birmingham and
OL,18,FLondon, but I don't want to go there,
OL,19,FI like to stay in a quiet place.
