OL,6,F"People are good people, they said
OL,7,Fthey will help us if anything happen
OL,8,Fthey say they will come out. They ask
OL,9,Fme if I am alright and if I want to
OL,10,Fstay."
OL,12,F"We planned to move somewhere else but
OL,13,Fthe neighbours said we needed to stay
OL,14,Fhere and we will support your family."
OL,16,FIn a statement police said: "Our
OL,17,Finvestigation is ongoing and local
OL,18,Fofficers are working closely with
OL,19,Fpartner agencies and support groups as
OL,20,Four enquiries continue.
